    "path": "README.md",
    "url": "https://github.com/example/toolkit/blob/main/README.md",
    "bytes": 700,
    "content": "# Toolkit\n\nToolkit helps developers generate typed API clients from OpenAPI specs.\n\n## Features\n\n- Generates typed clients from OpenAPI files\n- Keeps frontend clients aligned with backend API contracts\n\n## Installation\n\n```bash\nnpm install @example/toolkit\n```\n\n## Usage\n\n```bash\nnpx toolkit generate openapi.yaml\n```\n"
  },
